graph TD
    subgraph Live Inputs
        MIC[Vocal Mic] --> CH1[Ch1 Vocal Dry<br/>GATE dynamics]
        DI[Guitar DI] --> CH2[Ch2 Guitar Dry]
    end

    subgraph Vocal Outboard - Patchbay P1-P4
        CH1 -->|Bus 1 Vocal Send<br/>pre-fader, clean| OUT1[Wing Out 1 → P1]
        OUT1 --> HA73A[HA73 A<br/>Neve EQ / Color]
        HA73A -->|P2| WA76A[WA76 A<br/>1176 Compression<br/>Atk 3, Rel 7, 4:1]
        WA76A -->|P3| OPTO[Opto<br/>LA-2A Leveling<br/>Peak Red ~40%]
        OPTO -->|P4| CH17[Ch17 Vocal Processed<br/>DE-ES dynamics]
    end

    subgraph Guitar Outboard - Patchbay P5-P8
        CH2 -->|Bus 2 Guitar Send<br/>pre-fader, clean| OUT2[Wing Out 2 → P5]
        OUT2 --> HA73B[HA73 B<br/>Neve EQ / Color]
        HA73B -->|P6| WA76B[WA76 B<br/>1176 Compression<br/>Atk 5, Rel 6, 4:1]
        WA76B -->|P7| DIST[Distressor<br/>Leveling + Tape Sat<br/>4:1, Dist 2]
        DIST -->|P8| CH18[Ch18 Guitar Processed]
    end

    subgraph Recording - Clean to Logic
        CH17 -->|Bus 7 Vocal Rec<br/>pre-fader, clean| BUS7[Bus 7 Vocal Rec<br/>no TAPE]
        CH18 -->|Bus 8 Guitar Rec<br/>pre-fader, clean| BUS8[Bus 8 Guitar Rec<br/>no TAPE]
        BUS7 -->|USB| LOGIC[Logic Pro<br/>Primary Recorder]
        BUS8 -->|USB| LOGIC
    end

    subgraph Monitoring - Through Matrices to Model 12
        CH17 -->|send| MX2[MX2 Mix Vocal<br/>USB 33 → M12 Ch 1]
        CH18 -->|Bus 10 or 11| AMP[Bus 10 Rhythm Mon FX7 RACKAMP<br/>Bus 11 Lead Mon FX12 ANGEL<br/>amp sim added post-outboard]
        AMP --> MX34[MX3 Mix Rhythm USB 34<br/>MX4 Mix Lead USB 35]
        MX2 -->|USB 33-42| M12[Model 12<br/>Mixing Console]
        MX34 --> M12
    end

    subgraph Tape Returns - Logic Playback
        LOGIC -->|USB 17-26| TR[Ch25-32 Tape Returns]
        TR -->|Bus 3 Reverb| BUS3[Bus 3 Reverb<br/>FX2 PLATE]
        TR -->|Bus 10/11 for guitar| AMP2[Amp Sim<br/>same monitoring buses]
        TR -->|matrix sends| MX_TR[Matrices → Model 12]
    end

    subgraph Session Players
        SP[Logic Session Players<br/>Bass, Keys, Synth, Drums] -->|USB 9-16| CH9[Ch9-12]
        CH9 --> MX_SP[MX6 Bass / MX7 Drums / MX8 Piano]
        MX_SP --> M12
    end

    subgraph Tape Aux Loop - Mixing Phase
        M12_AUX[Model 12 AUX 1 Out] -->|analog| CH33[Ch33 Tape FX<br/>FX13 TAPE pre-insert<br/>FX6 TAPE-DL post-insert]
        CH33 -->|USR/3 POST → USB 38| M12_CH6[Model 12 Ch 6]
    end

    subgraph Model 12 Monitor Return
        M12 -->|USB 3/4| CH7[Ch7 Model 12 Mix]
        CH7 --> MAIN[Main 1<br/>Headphones / Speakers]
    end

    NOTE[Recording = clean outboard only. No tape, no amp sim baked in.<br/>Monitoring = through matrices to Model 12, not Main.<br/>Tape saturation = mixing phase via Model 12 AUX 1 loop.<br/>Solo Ch7 on Main to hear Model 12 mix. All buses OFF Main.]

